COMMITTEE AMENDMENT

COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to S.P. 510, L.D. 1282
1 SUMMARY
22 This amendment adds to the bill historic properties designated by comprehensive plans
33 to the eligibility requirements for grants for the preservation and restoration of historic
44 properties through the Maine Historic Preservation Commission. The amendment also
55 requires the Maine Historic Preservation Commission to include historic properties that
66 have been designated as historic properties by comprehensive plans in receiving funding
77 through bond proceeds authorized by Public Law 2023, chapter 653.
88 FISCAL NOTE REQUIRED
99 (See attached)
